726717f-a.title: Queens: Fresh Meadow Lane - Auburndale Lane
726717f-a.text:
Fresh Meadow Lane, north side, east of Auburndale Lane, showing the
J. Lawrence house of 1873. In 1909 it was the property of Dewitt and
Lott.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
